reviewText: Laugh out loud Funny. your gonnaa watch this over and over! in know i did . ONE OF if not THE funniest show on DVD

This show is amazing and I was so glad I got it for the price I did.  Ordered through Amazon so it came in a jif.  The seasons come shrink wrapped together so it is easy to tell that you got the right thing.  Order now laugh later.
WAS REALLY HAPPY TO LOCATE THE EARLY EPISODES OF THIS COMEDY SERIES.  IT ARRIVED IN GREAT CONDITION AND IN GREAT TIMIE. WOULD DEFINITELY USE THIS SELLER AGAIN.
Just a sharp, well-written comedy that appeals to a younger generation.  Can't wait to get Season 4 on DVD...enough said
